==Translingual==
===Etymology===
Formed from ''Magnoliaceae'' (Art 16 ''[[ICBN]]'')

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Magnoliophyta'''''
#{{botany}} the [[botanical name]] of a [[division]], within [[kingdom]] ''[[Plantae]]''. [[Circumscription]] of this division will vary with the [[taxonomic system]]: in the Cronquist system usually the [[angiosperm]]s or [[flowering plant]]s

